checks.prompt:
Synthesise the following security audit findings into an executive risk report:

CVE FINDINGS: {cve_input}
SECRETS FINDINGS: {secrets_input}
OWASP RESULTS: {owasp_input}

Produce:
1. Executive Summary (2 paragraphs, non-technical)
2. Risk Matrix (Critical/High/Medium/Low finding counts)
3. Top 5 priority actions with effort estimates
4. Overall risk posture: CRITICAL / HIGH / MEDIUM / LOW
5. 30-day remediation roadmap

Context: {retryContext}
